Gravtastic
==========

Easily add Gravatars to your application!


Example
=======

This goes in your model:

  class User < ActiveRecord::Base
    acts_as_gravatar_id :email
  end

This goes in your view

  = image_tag current_user.gravatar
  
and your done! If you want to customize the gravatar, just pass it some extra options:

  = image_tag current_user.gravatar(:width => 80, :height => 80)


